<!--
  Adaptive-icon MONOCHROME layer for Android 13+ themed icons. A single solid
  silhouette (the system recolors it to match the user's wallpaper-derived
  palette), so it must be one flat color with the meaning carried by SHAPE. The
  shield is solid and the play triangle is knocked out as negative space via
  evenOdd, so the mark still reads when tinted to a single hue. Same 66x66dp
  safe zone as the foreground. Shared 1:1 with the phone app.
-->
